	(text "IO — badge_hw_design.md §Buttons, §SAO, §Connectors.\nButtons → GND with RP2040 internal pullups. SAO 2×3 standard pinout.\nmicroSD on SPI0 (SCK=GP2, MOSI=GP3, MISO=GP4, CS=GP5).\n4.7k I2C pullups for SAO bus (RP2040 internal pulls are too weak)." (exclude_from_sim no) (at 25.00 25.00 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27)) (justify left top)) (uuid "2cd584a2-5771-4309-93c0-83001d2ae04e"))
